<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1037797" n="1"/> 
<opener><salute>Illustrissimo et Doctissimo Viro
    <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1156361761">Sebastiano Checozzi</rs></salute>
  <lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119166895">N. B.</rs></opener>
<p><lb/>Quem mihi multoties laudavit <add><rs type="person">amicus</rs> noster co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>unis</add> propensum Tuum in me
  <lb/>animum abunde satis perspexi ex <rs type="letter" key="B_991170517060005501">epistola</rs> Tua gratissima,
  <lb/>quam <date when="1719-02-23">ante paucos dies</date> mihi <del><gap/></del>tradidit idem
  <lb/>noster <rs type="person">amicus</rs>. Gratias proin ago maximas pro favore<del><gap/></del>
  <lb/>eximio, quo me, licet i<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>eren<del><gap/></del><add>t</add>em, dignari<add>s</add> <del><gap/></del>rogoque ut
  <lb/>Tibi vicissim persuadeas, me nihil <del><gap/></del><add>officii</add> intermissurum, <del><gap/></del><add>quo</add>
  <lb/><del><gap/></del>meam erga Te
  <lb/>et honestissima Tua merita observantiam declarare pos<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>sim. Hujus quidem sinceri affectus testimonium sit pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sens
  <lb/>epistola, in qua breviter et amice monebo, quid in solutio<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>ne Tua Problematis <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me propositi desiderem. Optavissem
  <lb/>sane ut laudatissimus iste Tuus conatus (pro quo solo me
  <lb/><del><gap/></del>Tibi <add>plurimum</add> obligatum profiteor) felicem omni ex parte
  <lb/>habuisset successum, sed credo <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>et id quam maxime doleo<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice>
  <lb/>adversam <add>illam</add>, qua Te <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> longo tempore affligi dicis, valetudinem
  <lb/>Te impediviss<del><gap/></del><add>e</add>, quo minus omnia attente considerare
  <lb/>potueris. Error Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> investigstionis in hoc consistit, quod <del><gap/></del>ponis
  <lb/>tempora <del><gap/></del>descensuum partialium esse ut vires in fine istor<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>um temporum agentes <add>si nempe <del><gap/></del>ista tempora sint proportionalia temporibus integrorum descensuum</add><supplied>,</supplied> quod etsi verum sit in nostro casu, sine
  <lb/>demonstratione tamen assumi non debet pro principio investi<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>gationis, siquidem de hoc tum demum constat postquam Curva
  <lb/>virium aut temporum inventa <del><gap/></del>est. Nempe si in figura
  <lb/>tua expon<choice><orig><g ref="#an">ā</g></orig><reg>an</reg></choice>t <del><gap/></del><add>recte</add> <formula>AC</formula>, <add><formula>aC</formula></add> temp<del><gap/></del><add>ora duorum</add> descensu<del><gap/></del><add>um</add> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> quiete usque ad
  <lb/>centrum, et <del><gap/></del><add>rect<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></add> <formula>AB</formula>, <add><formula>ab</formula></add> vi<del><gap/></del><add>res</add> in principio motus, absciss<del><gap/></del><add><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></add> autem
  <lb/><del><gap/></del><formula>AD</formula>, <add><formula>ad</formula></add> expon<choice><orig><g ref="#an">ā</g></orig><reg>an</reg></choice>t<del><gap/></del> 
  <pb facs="1037798" n="2"/> 
  <lb/><figure/> tempora partialia totis <formula>AC</formula>, <formula>aC</formula> proportionalia,
  <lb/>et applicat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> respectiv<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <formula>DE</formula>, <formula>de</formula>, exponant vires
  <lb/>in utroque descensu in fine istorum temporum
  <lb/>partialium agentes; non potest ex eo solo, quod
  <lb/>per conditionem Problematis vires prim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <formula ana="corr">AB</formula>, <formula>ab</formula>,
  <lb/>proportionales esse debeant temporibus integris
  <lb/><formula>AC</formula>, <formula>aC</formula>, statim inferri; quod etiam vires <formula>ED</formula>,
  <lb/><formula>ed</formula>, <del><gap/></del>iisdem temporibus integris <formula>AC</formula>, <formula>aC</formula>, aut partibus
  <lb/>ipsorum <formula>AD</formula>, <formula>ad</formula>, proportionales esse debeant; id est, non potest
  <lb/>ex similitudine tri<unclear>angu</unclear>lorum <formula>BAC</formula>, <formula>baC</formula> concludi similitudo
  <lb/>spatiorum curvilineorum <formula>BECA</formula>, <formula>beCa</formula>. Uno verbo,<del><gap/></del>
  <lb/>si Curv<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <formula>BEC</formula>, <formula>beC</formula> similes esse ponantur, inservient ill<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> tan<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>tum pro uno eodemque descensu mobilis ex eodem puncto quie<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>tis, et non pro duobus descensibus ex diversis locis. Levis ad
  <lb/>hanc rem attentio Te melius veritatem assertionis me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> docebit
  <lb/>quam ego nunc verbis facere possim; speroque Te re perpensa
  <lb/><del><gap/></del><add>comperturum</add>, Problema
  <lb/>difficilius esse, quam fortassis ipse expectaveras. Intelliges
  <lb/>etiam errare illos, qui dicunt, mihi nullum jus esse postu<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>landi <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> solutoribus ut methodum suam co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>unicent, cum multi
  <lb/>fuerint, et inter illos <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969 pers_DE-588-118509950">Patrui</rs> mei, qui inventa sua s<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>pe <del><gap/></del><add>sin</add>e de<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>monstratione aut analysi publicaverint; <add><del><gap/></del>tamen hoc ipsis vitio datum fuerit<supplied>;</supplied></add> horum enim exemp<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>lo tueri se non possunt illi, qui Problema meum null<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>
  <lb/>includere difficultatem affirmarunt, idque tantum non
  <lb/>Tyronibus ablegandum esse putarunt, me propterea contemtus
  <lb/>adversus Geometras Italos accusantes. Ego igitur nihil aliud ab
  <lb/>illis petivi, quam ut assertionem suam probarent et facilita<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>tem Problematis ostenderent, et sic calumni<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> notam, cujus 
  <pb facs="1037799" n="3"/> 
  <lb/>apud me rei sunt, <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> se depellerent. Ego quidem <choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> contrario exi<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>stimo, me Geometras Italos honore affecisse proponendo ipsis Pro<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>blema dignum ipsorum <del><gap/></del><add>studiis</add>. <del><gap/></del><add>Q</add>uod <add>autem</add> attinet
  <lb/>ad <rs type="biblio">Schediasma</rs> tuum (<rs type="biblio"><abbr>Tom.</abbr> XXIII<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> <abbr>art.</abbr> 5. Diarii</rs>) multa eruditione
  <lb/>rebusque scitu dignissimis refertum, quo nomine illud appellan<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>dum sit, de hoc non est cur disputemus, ne in Logomachiam inci<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>damus. Scis vocem hanc <hi rend="u">Solutio</hi> <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> congruit cum gr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ca
  <lb/>voce <hi rend="u">Analysis</hi><choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> duplice modo usurpari, vel pro responsione
  <lb/>ad qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>situm, vel pro ipsa investigatione Problematis, quam
  <lb/>alias analysin appellant. <del><gap/></del><add>Quum</add> si<!-- Kontrollieren, ob als gestrichen zu lesen --> <rs type="biblio">Schediasma</rs>
  <lb/><del><gap/></del>illud continere potius
  <lb/>demonstrationem solutionis <add>aut theorematis <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me citati<supplied>,</supplied> ex quo fluit illa Solutio</add><supplied>,</supplied> quam ipsam solutionem, hoc dixi
  <lb/>quia h<del><gap/></del><add>an</add>c appellationem scopo ipsius <rs type="biblio">schediasmatis</rs> convenientio<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>rem esse existimavi; siquidem scopus Tuus non erat dare re<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>sponsionem ad qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>situm <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c enim responsio jam nota erat
  <lb/>ex <rs type="biblio"><abbr>art<supplied>.</supplied></abbr> 11<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice><!-- Kontrollieren ob 11 oder II --> <abbr>Tom.</abbr> XXI</rs><choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> sed firmare eandem responsionem demonstra<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>tione.<del><gap/></del>
  <lb type="deleted"/><del><gap/></del>
  <lb type="deleted"/><del><gap/></del>
  <lb/><del><gap/></del>Tandem quod attinet ad meam<del><gap/></del>
  <lb/>hujus Problematis solutionem, eam<del><gap/></del> publicare statueram
  <lb/>sub forma responsionis ad <del><gap/></del>Tuam <rs type="letter">epistolam</rs>; sed quia Tu forsan
  <lb/><del><gap/></del><add>agnita</add> veritate objectionis me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Tuam <rs type="letter">epistolam</rs> publica<del><gap/></del><add>ri</add> noles,
  <lb/><del><gap/></del>expectabo <rs type="letter">responsum</rs> Tuum, quo me certiorem facies de Tua volun<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>tate, nihil enim suscipiam nisi quod in Tui honorem vergere possit.
  <lb/>Forsan altera illa Tua, cujus mentionem injicis, analysis nulli obje<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <lb break="no"/>ctioni obnoxia erit, quam si talem repetito examine deprehendes
  <lb/>mecumque co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>unicabis, <del><gap/></del>rem gratissimam <del><gap/></del>facies,
  <lb/>occasionemque <add>mihi</add> subministrabis, <add>ut</add> me verum eruditionis et virtu<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
  <pb facs="1037800" n="4"/>
  <lb break="no"/>tum Tuarum <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stimatorem publice demonstrare possim. Interim
  <lb/>precor Deum, ut meliorem Tibi restituat valetudinem, quo studia
  <lb/>h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c nostra <add>Geometrica</add>, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Tibi in deliciis esse gaudeo, pro voto excolere
  <lb/>et amplificare queas. </p> <closer><salute>Vale igitur optime et mihi fave. </salute> <dateline>Da<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc>
      <lb break="no"/>bam <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3171728">Patavii</rs> <abbr>a. d.</abbr> <date when="1719-03-07">7. Marti<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice> 1719</date>.</dateline></closer>
</div>
